verse.name: v1a
verse.lines:
The sun comes up
Its a new dawn
Its time to sing your song again
Whatever may past and whatever lies before me
Let me be singing till the evening comes

verse.name: v1b
verse.lines:
i have zoe
i have zoe
The spirit of God

I have Zoe
I have Zoe
The life of God is what we have
